tterly disapponting.  I get it, it's important for people to learn the lessons of history, but this is like smashing people in the face with a history book (simply turning Jews into ""magicals"" does not conceal the heavy-handed message).  It isn't original, or even interesting.  It's supposed to be a game, not a history lesson."
