76561197997984901,Recommended,237850,18388453,"Posted: 8 October, 2015",all,OrbitalBeetle,"The gameplay is mediocre at best and tedious at worst. But I don't care about that at all.The strong point of the series is the storytelling and the characters. For fans of the series, that is all that ultimately matters.If one hasn't played the prior games of the series, then start there first. Otherwise you will be missing parts of the the story, and that is like starting to read a book right in the middle - you start out without any emotional attachment to the characters and the events that happened before. And I don't think this series can be played in reversed chronological order either, you'd miss out bigtime."
